Package: grendelshiny
Type: Package
Title: Shared Styling for Grendel Shiny Apps
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Rolf", family = "Lindgren", email = "rolf@grendel.no", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Shared CSS and JavaScript helpers that give a family of Grendel
    Shiny apps a consistent turquoise-dark visual theme. Provides a base design
    system (layout, typography, form controls, sliders, tabs) and a small
    JavaScript utility for managing selectize dropdown state.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: htmltools
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
